For many wealthy investors, its history is the big attraction, although some 
developers are wary of being too brazenly commercial about this.

'Clients, international and German alike,
 value living on historical ground,' said Michael Ries of the property 
developer Pantera which is behind The Garden project and is the German 
partner to Sotheby's International Realty.

